# Threat Model Forge repository attributes.

# Render .tm7 diffs as readable structure and merge them semantically (instead of textual
# DataContract XML) via the tmforge diff/merge driver. Enable per clone, once:
#     git config diff.tmforge.textconv "tmforge diff --textconv"
#     git config merge.tmforge.name    "Threat Model Forge semantic merge"
#     git config merge.tmforge.driver  "tmforge merge %O %A %B %P"
# See docs/cli-reference.md (the `diff` and `merge` commands).
*.tm7 diff=tmforge merge=tmforge
